queries.sql: SELECT m.*,r.* FROM app_menu m LEFT JOIN app_role r ON r.menu_id = m.menu_id LEFT JOIN app_group g ON r.group_id = g.group_id WHERE r.group_id='1' AND m.deleted_at IS NULL AND m.aktif='1' AND r.akses_lihat='1' ORDER BY urutan ASC;
SELECT m.*,r.* FROM app_menu m LEFT JOIN app_role r ON r.menu_id = m.menu_id LEFT JOIN app_group g ON r.group_id = g.group_id WHERE m.prefik='data-unor-verifikator' ;

SELECT d1.*, d2.NamaUnor as nama_induk, status_v, status_a FROM dataunor d1 LEFT JOIN dataunor d2 ON d1.unor_induk = d2.UnorId LEFT JOIN unor_verifikator uva ON uva.unor_id_verifikator = d1.UnorId WHERE d1.cepat_kode<>'0' ORDER BY d1.no_urut ASC
